Use ahesion promoter. It's a clear spray that helps paint stick to
bare metal. Helps when you don't want to use a self etching primer or
sand the item.

http://www.sherwin-automotive.com/products/show_product.cfm?product=980&cat=39

Dupli and others have rattle-can versions as well.


 
